{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-services-js","path":"/services/tax-planning","result":{"data":{"wordpressWpServices":{"excerpt":"<p>Make sure you haven’t overlooked tax planning as an important part of building your wealth. We help you review the tax implications of all your financial decisions, including the types of retirement plans available to you and the capital gains you can incur.</p>\n","slug":"tax-planning","title":"Tax Planning","wordpress_id":477,"acf":{"work_with_us":"<p>We at Sherman Wealth Management want to work with you to make your goals and needs a reality. Whether you’re located in Maryland or Washington, DC, or if you’re across the country or world, we offer a complimentary 30-minute introductory call where we review your portfolio and financial goals and discuss ideas to get you on track to meeting those goals.</p>\n","content_blocks_services":[{"__typename":"WordPressAcf_regular_content","content_text":"<p>Taxes are a significant factor in building wealth so we work with you to help you review the tax implications of financial decisions, including the types of retirement plans you choose and capital gains you incur. Unlike many financial planners, we offer tax planning on an ongoing basis, to help you avoid costly mistakes as you build for your future.</p>\n<p>Particularly in your early-earning years, tax decisions can have a long-term effect on long term investment income.</p>\n<p><a href=\"/investment-planning\">Click here</a> to learn how we also help you with Investment Management and <a href=\"/retirement-planning\">here</a> for Retirement Planning.</p>\n<p>And <a href=\"./contact-us\">click here</a> to get started with a free consultation to learn the critical ways that tax choices can have a positive – or negative – effect on your financial future.</p>\n<p><img class=\"size-full wp-image-154 aligncenter\" src=\"https://shermandev.cydoniacloudserver.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Age-and-Net-worth-e1546675756500.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"619\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https://shermandev.cydoniacloudserver.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Age-and-Net-worth-e1546675756500.png 619w, https://shermandev.cydoniacloudserver.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Age-and-Net-worth-e1546675756500-300x194.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 619px) 100vw, 619px\" /></p>\n","id":"16eb23db-0eb0-541a-95fa-6e14839f5b920content_blocksWordPressAcf_regular_content"}]}},"wordpressWpApiMenusMenusItems":{"items":[{"classes":"","title":"Who we are","object_id":55,"url":"https://shermandev.cydoniacloudserver.com/who-we-are/","object_slug":"who-we-are","order":1,"wordpress_children":null},{"classes":"","title":"Services","object_id":1180,"url":"/services/overview","object_slug":"services","order":2,"wordpress_children":[{"wordpress_parent":1180,"classes":"","object_id":167,"object_slug":"financial-planning","title":"Financial Planning","type":"post_type","type_label":"Service"},{"wordpress_parent":1180,"classes":"","object_id":175,"object_slug":"investment-planning","title":"Investment Planning","type":"post_type","type_label":"Service"},{"wordpress_parent":1180,"classes":"","object_id":477,"object_slug":"tax-planning","title":"Tax Planning","type":"post_type","type_label":"Service"},{"wordpress_parent":1180,"classes":"","object_id":479,"object_slug":"retirement-planning","title":"Retirement Planning","type":"post_type","type_label":"Service"},{"wordpress_parent":1180,"classes":"","object_id":480,"object_slug":"estate-and-trust-planning","title":"Estate Planning","type":"post_type","type_label":"Service"},{"wordpress_parent":1180,"classes":"","object_id":478,"object_slug":"business-planning","title":"Business Planning","type":"post_type","type_label":"Service"},{"wordpress_parent":1180,"classes":"","object_id":1177,"object_slug":"services-fees","title":"Services Fees","type":"custom","type_label":"Custom Link"}]},{"classes":"","title":"Who we serve","object_id":65,"url":"https://shermandev.cydoniacloudserver.com/who-we-serve